Summary: 
 * Merge from HscdSupport--devel--0.8
 - Concentrate face type definitions in FacadeTraits class.
 - Switched to boost::add_const and boost::remove_const from boost/type_traits for Facade.hpp
   Instead of Const<T::Ptr> use FacadeTraits<typename boost::add_const<T>::type>::Ptr
   Instead of Mutable<T::Ptr> use FacadeTraits<typename boost::remove_const<T>::type>::Ptr
 - Provide boost::add_reference/remove_reference boost::add_pointer/remove_pointer for Facade.hpp
